<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A new option should be added to allow parsing of all subdirectories from a given one for source files.</p>

<p>Mainly this is intended to allow old gettext structures to be used within the gettext adapter without the need to extend it.</p>

<p>So additionally to the "scanDirectory" option the new option "scanSubDirectories" allows the directory to be named like</p>

<p>/<em>/"locale"/</em>/... which means all found source file in that sub-directory are included in this locale.</p>

